1147
01:18:27,400 --> 01:18:29,770
Keep your eye on that mayor.

1148
01:18:29,770 --> 01:18:31,100
What does he have
 to do with anything?

1149
01:18:34,060 --> 01:18:37,510
You'll see.

1150
